**Got another //divination//:
***//As you drift into the view of the spirit world, You see what look like blood cells moving through a blood vessel. The view zooms out to show a vein wrapped with little metal slivers. The view zooms out again to show what looks like an arm with a vine wrapped around it. The view travels up the vine and then changes to look like sthe thorny stalk of a rose, then the view shifts upward to show a rose in bloom. As the rose blooms, the pistils of the flower warp into faintly glowing tentacles that lash out, stabbing through figures that look like people with a brutal slicing sound. As the figures seem to become desiccated, the flower's petals bloom more brightly, becoming from a dull gray color to a vivid blood red.//
